\* A slightly harder toy that requires branching *\
Minimize
 obj: x1 + x2 + x3 + x4 + x5 + x6 + x7 + x8
Subject To
 c1: x1 + x2 + x3 + x4 + x5 + x6 + x7 + x8 >= 2.6
 c2: x1 + x2 + x3 <= 1.4
 c3: x4 + x5 + x6 <= 1.4
 c4: x7 + x8 <= 1.4
Bounds
 0 <= x1 <= 1
 0 <= x2 <= 1
 0 <= x3 <= 1
 0 <= x4 <= 1
 0 <= x5 <= 1
 0 <= x6 <= 1
 0 <= x7 <= 1
 0 <= x8 <= 1
Binaries
 x1 x2 x3 x4 x5 x6 x7 x8
End

